---
---

<section id="about" class="relative pt-16 pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid bg-grid-fade opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="container-k relative">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="chip mb-6">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-magenta"></span>
          About Kinvrs
        </div>
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-white" data-reveal="up">
          The <span class="text-gradient">Creative</span><br/>Voyager.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-light">
        <p>
          Across today's digital world, ideas move fast and possibilities expand by the minute.
          Creators, teams and communities look for spaces where imagination can grow and
          technology quietly supports their ambition.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is where <span class="text-white font-medium">Kinvrs</span> steps in — turning complex
          infrastructure into something intuitive, reliable and full of creative potential.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-xl italic font-light border-l-2 border-electric pl-6">
          "Boldly crafting tech infrastructure that powers play, creation,
          connection, and beyond."
        </p>

        {/* Personality traits */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 pt-6" data-reveal-stagger>
          {[
            ['Imaginative', 'future-focused'],
            ['Curious', 'exploratory'],
            ['Craft-driven', 'precise'],
            ['Bold', 'grounded'],
          ].map(([a, b]) => (
            <div class="glass p-4">
              <div class="text-white font-semibold">{a}</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white/50">{b}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
